21
00:00:59.942 --> 00:01:02.124
NOVA:  What exactly is a 'log'?

22
00:01:02.424 --> 00:01:05.380
VEGA:  A diary the system keeps. A Windows Event

23
00:01:05.380 --> 00:01:07.903
Log, a syslog, a tool like Splunk -

24
00:01:07.903 --> 00:01:08.624
same idea.

25
00:01:09.674 --> 00:01:12.234
VEGA:  AU-2 chooses what's worth logging.

26
00:01:12.534 --> 00:01:14.450
NULL:  So I'll just delete the logs when I'm

27
00:01:14.450 --> 00:01:14.709
