28
00:01:16.174 --> 00:01:19.934
VEGA:  Not so fast. AU-9 protects the logs themselves.

29
00:01:20.234 --> 00:01:23.096
NOVA:  So the Null can't quietly rewrite history.

30
00:01:24.146 --> 00:01:26.874
ARCHIVIST:  Identify the types of events that the system

31
00:01:26.874 --> 00:01:29.292
is capable of logging in support of the

32
00:01:29.292 --> 00:01:30.222
audit function:

33
00:01:31.272 --> 00:01:33.142
VEGA:  A log no one reads, or one that

34
00:01:33.142 --> 00:01:35.072
can be erased, is no log at all.

35
00:01:41.572 --> 00:01:44.865
VEGA:  The Chronicler's oath. Every footstep written; no page

36
00:01:44.865 --> 00:01:45.292
erased.

37
00:01:46.342 --> 00:01:49.302
VEGA:  The Healer, System and Information Integrity.

38
00:01:49.602 --> 00:01:52.606
NOVA:  It finds the rot, cures the sickness, and

39
00:01:52.606 --> 00:01:54.144
keeps the truth true.

40
00:01:54.444 --> 00:01:57.899
VEGA:  In reality, that's patching flaws, blocking malicious code,

41
00:01:57.899 --> 00:02:01.471
monitoring for intrusions, and verifying nothing was tampered

42
00:02:01.471 --> 00:02:01.764
with.

43
00:02:02.814 --> 00:02:07.014
VEGA:  SI-2 is flaw remediation, the discipline of patching.

44
00:02:09.314 --> 00:02:11.991
VEGA:  And SI-4 watches the system for signs of

45
00:02:11.991 --> 00:02:12.794
an intruder.

46
00:02:13.094 --> 00:02:18.013
NULL:  Another tower turns? Tedious. Every chain of watchers

47
00:02:18.013 --> 00:02:20.704
has a blind link - and I will

48
00:02:20.704 --> 00:02:22.189
slip through it.

49
00:02:23.239 --> 00:02:26.624
NULL:  Six days I moved in your shadows before

50
00:02:26.624 --> 00:02:28.534
a single tower turned.

51
00:02:28.834 --> 00:02:29.616
NOVA:  Six days?!

52
00:02:29.916 --> 00:02:32.456
VEGA:  Six days - but SI-4 saw the anomaly,

53
00:02:32.456 --> 00:02:35.067
and AU-9 kept the logs he tripped. He

54
