94
00:05:03.259 --> 00:05:05.299
VEGA:  And who runs toward the fire?

95
00:05:05.599 --> 00:05:09.475
Which family detects, contains, and recovers from a

96
00:05:09.475 --> 00:05:10.007
breach?

97
00:05:10.307 --> 00:05:14.479
Your options. A. IR - Incident Response. B.

98
00:05:14.479 --> 00:05:17.875
AU - Audit. C. AC - Access Control.

99
00:05:18.175 --> 00:05:21.077
NOVA:  Pause here and lock in your answer.

100
00:05:28.127 --> 00:05:30.907
VEGA:  The answer is A. IR - Incident Response.

101
00:05:30.907 --> 00:05:34.730
Incident Response is the family that detects, contains,

102
00:05:34.730 --> 00:05:36.607
and recovers from a breach.

103
00:05:37.657 --> 00:05:40.641
NOVA:  Notebook: assume they got in, then see them,

104
00:05:40.641 --> 00:05:42.879
heal the system, and answer fast.

105
00:05:43.179 --> 00:05:46.459
VEGA:  Seen, healed, and answered. The towers hold.

106
00:05:46.759 --> 00:05:49.534
NULL:  Then I'll turn your own people against you.

107
00:05:49.834 --> 00:05:51.891
VEGA:  Then we ride to the Keepers of the

108
00:05:51.891 --> 00:05:52.194
Pact.
